  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dear players and adventurers:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>We are a small group of independent game developers. We are trying to make independent games in some different ways.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Although we have experienced some hardships and our development speed is limited, we are still working hard.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>You are welcome to leave messages in various ways and tell us your thoughts and opinions about this game.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>We will take seriously every player's suggestions, ideas, and even complaints. All of them have extremely high value and are important bases and references for our iterative updates.</strong><br> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088410/extras/11ea0a04c607be3daf545dd43d24b5c4.avif?t=1755056182\" width=614 height=108 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088410/extras/971d6e6d51dfbfe27f4f5b71126a6b9f.poster.avif?t=1755056182\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088410/extras/971d6e6d51dfbfe27f4f5b71126a6b9f.webm?t=1755056182\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088410/extras/971d6e6d51dfbfe27f4f5b71126a6b9f.mp4?t=1755056182\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>Create the ultimate 2D pixel-based battle experience in the name of ACT!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088410/extras/6c6abf9a4250e698c5a69b6780679b4b.avif?t=1755056182\" width=614 height=108 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088410/extras/ff72bc24742d918eb7c4dbd83ad4a9ec.poster.avif?t=1755056182\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088410/extras/ff72bc24742d918eb7c4dbd83ad4a9ec.webm?t=1755056182\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088410/extras/ff72bc24742d918eb7c4dbd83ad4a9ec.mp4?t=1755056182\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>This world provides a variety of combinations of weapons and skills, each of which can bring different strategies and combat experiences.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>At the same time, it also combines the characteristics of horizontal action games to create secrets for this world.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088410/extras/04d5300045e26252f821e834659695be.avif?t=1755056182\" width=614 height=108 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088410/extras/bdebc306124775ec701ec2e3ae7ccee9.poster.avif?t=1755056182\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088410/extras/bdebc306124775ec701ec2e3ae7ccee9.webm?t=1755056182\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088410/extras/bdebc306124775ec701ec2e3ae7ccee9.mp4?t=1755056182\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>This world provides a wide variety of equipment affixes, which can be assembled into various attribute tactics.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Use such a mechanism to pay tribute to the pursuit of the sword and magic era.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088410/extras/5be3916a5630e5524a0515c482163d2b.avif?t=1755056182\" width=614 height=108 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088410/extras/98e9c28a9e6aad9a4f4901a35ce87b4f.poster.avif?t=1755056182\" width=614 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088410/extras/98e9c28a9e6aad9a4f4901a35ce87b4f.webm?t=1755056182\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088410/extras/98e9c28a9e6aad9a4f4901a35ce87b4f.mp4?t=1755056182\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>This world has both hierarchy and repeated deaths. The way of progress requires you and me to pursue.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Paying tribute is also progressing.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088410/extras/58107d0a16fadb4cddabaa36348b3c18.avif?t=1755056182\" width=614 height=108 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088410/extras/0231464ea20fcd1ae679dd69b8646471.poster.avif?t=1755056182\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088410/extras/0231464ea20fcd1ae679dd69b8646471.webm?t=1755056182\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088410/extras/0231464ea20fcd1ae679dd69b8646471.mp4?t=1755056182\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>Explore and challenge this world with a tarot-style collection to fill your loot!</strong></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dear players and adventurers:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>We are a small group of independent game developers. We are trying to make independent games in some different ways.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Although we have experienced some hardships and our development speed is limited, we are still working hard.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>You are welcome to leave messages in various ways and tell us your thoughts and opinions about this game.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>We will take seriously every player's suggestions, ideas, and even complaints. All of them have extremely high value and are important bases and references for our iterative updates.</strong><br> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088410/extras/11ea0a04c607be3daf545dd43d24b5c4.avif?t=1755056182\" width=614 height=108 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088410/extras/971d6e6d51dfbfe27f4f5b71126a6b9f.poster.avif?t=1755056182\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088410/extras/971d6e6d51dfbfe27f4f5b71126a6b9f.webm?t=1755056182\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088410/extras/971d6e6d51dfbfe27f4f5b71126a6b9f.mp4?t=1755056182\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>Create the ultimate 2D pixel-based battle experience in the name of ACT!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088410/extras/6c6abf9a4250e698c5a69b6780679b4b.avif?t=