/strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Use such a mechanism to pay tribute to the pursuit of the sword and magic era.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088410/extras/5be3916a5630e5524a0515c482163d2b.avif?t=1755056182\" width=614 height=108 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088410/extras/98e9c28a9e6aad9a4f4901a35ce87b4f.poster.avif?t=1755056182\" width=614 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088410/extras/98e9c28a9e6aad9a4f4901a35ce87b4f.webm?t=1755056182\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088410/extras/98e9c28a9e6aad9a4f4901a35ce87b4f.mp4?t=1755056182\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>This world has both hierarchy and repeated deaths. The way of progress requires you and me to pursue.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Paying tribute is also progressing.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088410/extras/58107d0a16fadb4cddabaa36348b3c18.avif?t=1755056182\" width=614 height=108 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088410/extras/0231464ea20fcd1ae679dd69b8646471.poster.avif?t=1755056182\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088410/extras/0231464ea20fcd1ae679dd69b8646471.webm?t=1755056182\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"